ravities, however the results are still compatible with\nthe observational data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Oct 2018 18:02:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Feb 2019 19:05:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-20"}
