ited on metallic\nsubstrates, and assess the required conditions to obtain Kondo lattices in\nsuperlattices. We unveil a unique pathway between Kondo quenching and Mott\nlocalization, and identify a non-trivial charge density wave phase emerging\nfrom the competition of charge localization and Kondo physics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Oct 2018 20:01:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 21 Oct 2018 18:03:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 24 Oct 2018 11:19:39 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 2 Nov 2018 09:16:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-05"}
