ution even in the presence of the\ncollective mode, and within the same framework, we consider whether and how the\ndouble magicity of the 78Ni nucleus is restored, which is also of keen interest\nfrom the perspective of nucleosynthesis in explosive stellar processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Oct 2018 04:17:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Dec 2018 13:15:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 21 Jan 2019 16:10:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-23"}
