e that the metal spheres can be tuned to\noptimal absorption at a particular size at a particular frequency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Oct 2018 09:33:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Nov 2018 10:53:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-13"}
